title: Partnership
description: You can be part of creating a better future through backing us in one of the following ways:
text1: If you know a company or person that uses the latest technology to make a better womorrow, something. Real special to share with the society - let us know!
text2: Do you want to be part of making a tech imprint Join us as a partner!
text3: We will host Tech Imprint Arena all around the Nordics and are always in the need of people who can run the show with Us! Do you have the perfect place the be in the middle of the city? Or do you want to join the team? Let us know!
